title: Snake Eyes
description: A mysterious lone fighter, known only as \"Snake Eyes\", is welcomed into and trained by an ancient Japanese ninja clan called the Arashikage, but finds his loyalties being tested when secrets from his past are revealed, as he eventually goes on the path to become the famous G.I. Joe hero.

imdbInfo.ratingReason: Rated PG-13 for sequences of strong violence and brief strong language
